President Samia Suluhu Hassan has on Sunday appointed Brigadier General Yohana Ocholla Mabongo Â to be the new chairman of the Tanzania Postal Corporation (TPC) board of directors. Brigadier General Mabongo is the Head of ICT, Ministry of Defense and National Service. A statement released by the Director of Communications, Zuhura Yunus said the appointment of Brigadier General Mabongo took effect from February 24, 2022.